Hunter- SOLO
- The hunter starts on a team at the start of the game. They have all the same powers as a warrior, but they have a other motive.
- At the start of the game, the bounty hunter is given a name of a member not their team. They only win the game if that person is permanently dead before the hunter is dead.
- The hunter is also allowed to pick a permanent disguise at the start of the game.
- The hunter does not exit the game if they win, and can stay and continue to help their teams. They also don't have the benifit of a solo forge or a unlocked market.
- Has no abilities, and no cooldowns.
- Respawns in 2 phases.
